comments: Ingles (UTA) absorbs the initial body contact with Siakam (TOR) when the two players come together during the drive. He then makes marginal contact with Siakam and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Ibaka (TOR) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Bogdanovic's (UTA) path and he is firming up when the contact occurs during the pick.
Conley (UTA) initiates the contact by clamping Anunoby's (TOR) arm during the rebound and the contact affects his FOM.
Lowry (TOR) makes contact to Gobert's (UTA) arm that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Ibaka (TOR) is not established in O'Neale's (UTA) path during the pick and delivers contact.
Anunoby (TOR) makes contact with the ball and cleanly blocks Gobert's (UTA) shot attempt near the rim.
Prior to the contact with the ball, O'Neale (UTA) moves from point A to point B and delivers contact to Siakam's (TOR) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ibaka (TOR) briefly places a hand on Mitchell's (UTA) arm as he gathers the ball but he immediately removes it during the driving shot attempt. The contact is marginal.
Anunoby (TOR) delivers contact to Gobert's (UTA) neck area in transition and affects his FOM.
After Ibaka (TOR) legally absorbs the contact during the screen, Clarkson (UTA) makes marginal contact that doesn't affect his ability to maintain position.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.

The game clock starts to run before Siakam (TOR) receives the inbound pass. The play was not reviewable. The trigger for a clock malfunction review is when officials are reasonably certain that the game clock malfunctioned and a play concludes (i) with no time remaining on the clock (0:00) at the end of any period or (ii) at a point when the game officials believe that actual time may have expired in any period.
Siakam (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position on Clarkson (UTA).
Siakam (TOR) makes incidental high-five contact with Clarkson (UTA) after the release of the ball on his jump shot attempt.
Mitchell (UTA) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Bogdanovic (UTA) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
